      <h1>Counter-Strike</h1>
      <center>
        <h3>Release Date: Nov 1, 2000</h3>
      </center>
      <b>Windows</b>
      <b>Mac</b>
      <b>Linux</b>
    </div>
    <div class="modFlex">
      <p>"Play the world's number 1 online action game. Engage in an incredibly realistic brand of terrorist warfare in
        this wildly popular team-based game. Ally with teammates to complete strategic missions. Take out enemy sites.
        Rescue hostages. Your role affects your team's success. Your team's success affects your role."</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
